{"type": "article", "id": 24738, "title": "用建筑材料的蓝牙音响", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-31T06:52:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153225jtawyPToAN0xqei3.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款蓝牙音响用了多种材料，下面是混凝土底座，中间一层有黄铜丝，而在音响上面还有一层木头，很现代。设计师将它取名为“Pavilion”，意为凉亭，以呼应其中使用的常见于建筑的材料。黄铜丝的一段让底座和扬声器略有分开，让它有点像一个话筒。有黑白两色，售价 339 美元，<a href=\"https://hultdesign.com/?variant=13961169924\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153221ncBsHGFECSdyxfYi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153223lbMWcuOie1Qsr62a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 250px; width: 375px; left: 575px; top: 1001px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153223psLaxXJuhAl6OIcM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153224o5ZlbDAFreh7LiV1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}